## Task

Add non-intrusive interstitial ads between levels.

## Implementation

### Frequency Logic

```javascript
const Ads = {
  config: {
    interstitialEnabled: true,
    interstitialFrequency: 3, // Show every N rounds
    maxAdsPerHour: 5
  },

  state: {
    roundsSinceAd: 0,
    adsShownThisHour: 0,
    lastAdTime: null
  },

  shouldShowInterstitial() {
    if (this.isPremium()) return false;
    if (this.adsShownThisHour >= this.config.maxAdsPerHour) return false;

    this.state.roundsSinceAd++;
    return this.state.roundsSinceAd >= this.config.interstitialFrequency;
  }
};
```

### Placement

- Show between levels (after Level Complete closed)
- Skippable after 5 seconds
- Never during gameplay

### Rate Limiting

- Maximum 5 ads per hour
- Counter resets hourly

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Interstitial shows every 3 levels
- [ ] Skip button appears after 5 seconds
- [ ] Max 5 per hour enforced
- [ ] Premium users never see interstitials
- [ ] Counter tracks correctly
- [ ] No ads during active gameplay
- [ ] Graceful handling if ad fails to load
